<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="encouragement-n">encouragement <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ɪn'kʌrɪdʒmənt/    美 /ɪn'kɜːrɪdʒmənt/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>鼓励；激励；起激励作用的事物：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>With her encouragement, I decided to seize the opportunity. 
在她的鼓励下，我决定抓住这次机会。</p><footer>人教⑧ – 3</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Their words were a great <strong>encouragement to</strong> me. 
他们的话对我是极大的鼓励。</p></div></div>